reviewText: Stars Nena, the German Singer of "99 Luft Balloons". I had no idea she was also an actress, so I took a chance on this. You will need a all-region dvd player to play it and if you can't speak German, no worries. You can listen to it in English. This is kind of a musical, with Nena and others singing. Good music, some of which I recognize from her albums. This is a must have for Nena fans!
